# TravelPlan: Fully accessible Barcelona trip for 2 from Munich, 5–10 September 2026

| Day 1 — 2026-09-05 — Arrival and accessible hotel check-in | Day 2 — 2026-09-06 — Sagrada Família and Sant Pau | Day 3 — 2026-09-07 — Park Güell and accessible Gràcia | Day 4 — 2026-09-08 — Accessible beach and Poblenou food | Day 5 — 2026-09-09 — Passeig de Gràcia Gaudí icons and tapas | Day 6 — 2026-09-10 — Departure to Munich |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **1. Pre-flight accessible lunch in Munich** [meal] 13:00–14:00 @ Munich, Germany (€60.00) — Accessible lunch in Munich before heading to the airport. Choose a familiar step-free restaurant or airport-area option; keep the day low-stress before evening departure. — Links: [link 1](https://www.munich-airport.com/accessible-travel-260945) | **1. Accessible hotel stay: ILUNION Barcelona, 5 nights** [lodging] 01:00–01:05 @ Hotel ILUNION Barcelona, Carrer de Ramon Turró, 196-198, 08005 Barcelona (€1250.00) — Five-night stay in an adapted room. ILUNION Barcelona is reported to have 9 adapted rooms, step-free entrance, elevators, roll-in showers with fold-down seats and grab rails, and accessible public facilities. — Links: [link 1](https://www.enableholidays.com/ilunion-barcelona), [link 2](https://wheeltheworld.com/accessible-hotels/spain/barcelona/ilunion-hotels?srsltid=AfmBOooe1NjydKeSbLK3JOMXZXZiKzoHW7TAEVCWX-YpOLTkrkvgSAM_) | **1. Hotel breakfast** [meal] 08:30–09:15 @ Hotel ILUNION Barcelona (€30.00) — Breakfast at the hotel to keep the morning low-stress before Park Güell’s hilly terrain. — Links: [link 1](https://www.enableholidays.com/ilunion-barcelona) | **1. Hotel breakfast** [meal] 09:00–09:45 @ Hotel ILUNION Barcelona (€30.00) — Breakfast at hotel before beach day; ask reception to reconfirm current assisted bathing service hours. — Links: [link 1](https://www.enableholidays.com/ilunion-barcelona) | **1. Hotel breakfast** [meal] 09:00–09:45 @ Hotel ILUNION Barcelona (€30.00) — Hotel breakfast before a concentrated Passeig de Gràcia architecture day. — Links: [link 1](https://www.enableholidays.com/ilunion-barcelona) | **1. Check out and adapted taxi to BCN airport** [transport] 04:45–05:35 @ Hotel ILUNION Barcelona to Barcelona-El Prat Airport (€45.00) — Early check-out and pre-booked ramp-equipped taxi to BCN. Arrive about 2 hours before departure to allow Aena PRM assistance from check-in/security to aircraft seat. — Links: [link 1](https://wheelieguides.com/en/barcelona/transportation/airport/) |
